<p>
<note n="0423001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0423001">Gotama 應為辟支佛之名。</note>
<note n="0426001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0426001">Anātha 諒係辟支佛名，但以正覺者佛陀相稱（Buddha）。</note>
</p>
